I forked this project cos I really like the idea.

= INSTALL

$ sudo aptitude install sqlite3 libsqlite3-ruby
$ sudo gem install sinatra  dm-sqlite-adapter  data_mapper sqlite3-ruby
$ ./main.rb  # made it exectuable :-)

